room_title: Escape room "Riddler's Challenge" by Escape Room NJ in New York
room_description: The Riddler has lured you into his Funhouse with an invitation to a party, who can resist a party?! Some parties you would die just to get into, this one could be the exact opposite! You have 60 Minutes to figure out all of his many riddles, puzzles and mental challenges before the lethal gas fills the room and you take your last breath......
